[22/12/2019 23:27:51] <font color="#ffffff">Sin conocer el idioma,</font>
[22/12/2019 23:27:51] <font color="#ffffff">sin conocer a nadie.</font>
[22/12/2019 23:27:53] <font color="#ffffff">Una cosa era clara,</font>
